process the condition of conflicts

00:09:32.750 --> 00:09:36.660
within which all kinds of social
historical process takes place.

00:09:36.660 --> 00:09:38.180
So from these, it's kind

00:09:38.180 --> 00:09:43.080
of a conceptual framework why
globalization, why the Jesuits,

00:09:43.080 --> 00:09:46.700
