challenged this claim, that indeed,

00:10:20.540 --> 00:10:23.170
they were the first
organized group in history

00:10:23.170 --> 00:10:26.480
to think and to act globally.

00:10:26.480 --> 00:10:33.780 position:56%
Arguably for over two hundred
